  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"注：难度评级⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐为顶尖（清北复交人级别），推荐指数综合考虑招生规模、复试线、淘汰率和竞争压力。以上数据均为2025年口径，仅供参考。","font":"宋体","size":"9pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},

  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"1.5 上海财经大学（续）— 补充图片","bold":true,"size":"8pt","font":"宋体","color":"FFFFFF"}},

  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"五、综合推荐与备考建议","align":"center","bold":true,"size":"16pt","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"黑体","font":"黑体","spaceBefore":"18pt","spaceAfter":"6pt","lineSpacing":"1.5x"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"5.1 报考难度梯队","align":"left","bold":true,"size":"14pt","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"黑体","font":"黑体","spaceBefore":"12pt","spaceAfter":"3pt","lineSpacing":"1.5x"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"第一梯队（地狱难度）：复旦大学（大数据学院）、上海交通大学、南京大学、武汉大学、中国人民大学。复试线高、名额少、报录比极高。适合数学基础扎实、抗压能力强的顶尖考生。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"第二梯队（高难度）：华东师范大学、华中科技大学、苏州大学、对外经济贸易大学、中央财经大学。复试线350-370，招生规模中等，报录比4:1-10:1。适合学习成绩优异的考生。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"第三梯队（中等难度）：北京师范大学（珠海）345分/237人、上海财经大学323分/93人、中南财经政法大学323分/99人、浙江财经大学345分/90人。招生规模大、复试线相对友好、上岸概率高。适合求稳或跨考考生。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},

  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"5.2 针对浙江财经大学本科背景的建议","align":"left","bold":true,"size":"14pt","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"黑体","font":"黑体","spaceBefore":"12pt","spaceAfter":"3pt","lineSpacing":"1.5x"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"优势分析：浙江财经大学在长三角地区具有较高的认可度，尤其在财经统计领域。学校应统专业本身实力较强（国家级特色专业），本科课程覆盖了贾俊平《统计学》、茆诗松《概率论与数理统计》等考研核心内容。备考432统计学有一定基础优势。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"冲刺推荐：华东师范大学（报录比3.4:1，统考65人，性价比最高的985）、中央财经大学（211、报录比4.8:1、学费仅2.5万/年）、华中科技大学（统考31人、复试线365分较稳定）。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"稳妥选择：北京师范大学（珠海）（招生237人，上岸概率最高）中南财经政法大学（扩招至177人，323分复试线）、浙江财经大学本校（地缘优势+学费1万/年）。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},

  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"5.3 备考策略","align":"left","bold":true,"size":"14pt","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"黑体","font":"黑体","spaceBefore":"12pt","spaceAfter":"3pt","lineSpacing":"1.5x"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"（1）数学三（303）：应统考研的核心拉分科目。建议目标130+，重点突破高等数学和概率论。线性代数近年难度上升，不可轻视。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"（2）432统计学：各校自命题但知识点高度重合。核心书目：贾俊平《统计学》（第七版）、茆诗松《概率论与数理统计教程》。部分学校（上交、上财）考英语（一），需特别注意。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},
  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"（3）复试准备：多数学校复试占比30%-50%。武汉大学曾有396分被淘汰的案例，表明复试（尤其是笔试）不容忽视。建议提前准备Python/R编程、统计学基础面试问答。","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"宋体","font":"宋体","size":"12pt","firstLineIndent":"0.74cm","lineSpacing":"1.5x","spaceAfter":"3pt"}},

  {"command":"add","parent":"/body","type":"paragraph","props":{"text":"参考文献","align":"center","bold":true,"size":"14pt","font.latin":"Times New Roman","font.ea":"黑体","font":"黑体","spaceBefore":"18pt","spaceAfter":"6pt","lineSpacing":"1.5x"}},
